38
00:04:08,639 --> 00:04:12,919
 However, we met again. 

39
00:04:15,720 --> 00:04:17,460
Are you angry?

40
00:04:17,460 --> 00:04:21,280
♫  The more I care, the greater the pain  ♫

41
00:04:21,280 --> 00:04:23,559
I thought about it the whole night yesterday.

42
00:04:23,559 --> 00:04:28,119
How many obstacles will we face if we are together?

43
00:04:28,119 --> 00:04:29,920
Shen Dongyang.

44
00:04:29,920 --> 00:04:31,439
My eldest brother.

45
00:04:31,439 --> 00:04:33,559
My father.

46
00:04:33,559 --> 00:04:35,820
All the old men in the Jiang family.

47
00:04:36,799 --> 00:04:40,400
The names of different people kept appearing in my mind.

48
00:04:40,400 --> 00:04:44,799
All of them were telling me to forget it.

49
00:04:44,799 --> 00:04:47,860
It's not worth it for a man.

50
00:04:47,860 --> 00:04:49,220
♫  All right  ♫

51
00:04:49,220 --> 00:04:52,780
♫  I'm the invisible paramour   ♫

52
00:04:52,780 --> 00:04:55,840
♫  I'm pitiful  ♫

53
00:04:57,559 --> 00:04:59,679
I'm not good enough.

54
00:05:02,080 --> 00:05:04,199
That's not the case.

55
00:05:04,199 --> 00:05:05,720
It's me.

56
00:05:06,380 --> 00:05:09,040
Every time I feel like giving up,

57
00:05:09,040 --> 00:05:11,550
I can't help but think

58
00:05:12,410 --> 00:05:15,720
what would have happened if you hadn't avoided the bullet yesterday,

59
00:05:16,600 --> 00:05:22,559
if there was no longer anything between us, and if Fu Cheng no longer existed in this world.

60
00:05:22,559 --> 00:05:24,860
I thought about many possible situations.

61
00:05:26,319 --> 00:05:31,520
A moment ago, I finally understood why I thought about all these situations.

62
00:05:37,960 --> 00:05:39,919
I don't want to lose you.

63
00:05:58,559 --> 00:06:00,180
Yingxian,

64
00:06:02,444 --> 00:06:04,383
I can't go with you.

65
00:06:07,480 --> 00:06:09,559
I am just an ordinary person.

66
00:06:11,160 --> 00:06:16,370
I will also get angry and jealous

67
