115
00:11:19,280 --> 00:11:22,240
Tell me how Father fell.

116
00:11:22,240 --> 00:11:24,040
Did you do it?

117
00:11:24,040 --> 00:11:26,439
Sister, I didn't do it.

118
00:11:26,439 --> 00:11:28,040
